	dprr:hasNoteText "Sent to Thrace to return to King Cotys his son and the other Thracian hostages (Liv. 45.42.11)." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/2688> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #2688" ;
